Lifestream — Firebase Architecture & Prototype Plan
TL;DR: Lifestream is a lifecycle reminder app (think: “remind me to renew my passport, rotate tires, replace HVAC filter”). This plan maps the full spec onto Firebase-native services, with a realistic phased build approach.

1. Core App Concept & User Flows
What Lifestream Does
Manages time-sensitive life events (documents, appliances, health, subscriptions) with smart reminders, auto-detection, and escalating nudges — all automated after initial setup.
