Dynamic Interval Engine

function generateIntervals(category: ReminderCategory, daysUntilExpiry: number): number[] {
  const baseIntervals: Record<ReminderCategory, number[]> = {
    identity:  [180, 90, 60, 30, 14, 7, 3, 1],
    vehicle:   [60, 30, 14, 7, 3, 1],
    health:    [30, 14, 7, 3, 1],
    finance:   [30, 14, 7, 1],
    home:      [90, 30, 7, 1],
    legal:     [90, 30, 14, 7, 1],
    custom:    [30, 7, 1],
  };
  
  // Only return intervals that are still in the future
  return baseIntervals[category].filter(d => d <= daysUntilExpiry);
}


Smart Deferral Logic

User snoozes → snoozeCount++
  if snoozeCount >= maxSnoozes:
    → escalate urgencyLevel
    → notify shared vault members (if any)
    → send email fallback (via Firebase Email Extension)
  else:
    → schedule next nudge in 24h OR end of quiet hours


